short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This Extension Will Customize Your New Tab Experience.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Transform your new tab experience with "Searching For A Higher Cause!" Choose from a variety of charities and make a difference just by searching the web. With each search, "Searching For A Higher Cause" donates to the charity of your choice at no cost to you. Simply select your preferred cause, and "Searching For A Higher Cause" will personalize your new tab with the charity's logo and direct your searches through their supported search engine. Every search helps make the world a better place!

By clicking "Add to chrome", I accept and agree to installing the "Searching For A Higher Cause" extension and setting Chrome New Tab to "Searching For A Higher Cause" page provided by the service and the Terms of Use at https://smilestab.info/t-o-s/ and Privacy Policy at https://smilestab.info/privacy-policy/
